---
title: Sticky Haloumi & Bombay Potatoes with Garden Salad & Slivered Almonds
description: Sweet chilli sauce is a crowd favourite and we want to put it on everything! Haloumi is up next and once again, this sauce has
outdone itself. The salty haloumi gets a little sweeter and the potatoes get a decadent sprinkling of Mumbai spice, what more
could you ask for?

